java.lang.Object

          com.google.calendar.interoperability.connectorplugin.base.HackedSSLSocketFactory

public class HackedSSLSocketFactory
extends SSLSocketFactory

This class is a modified version of the standard SSL socket factory that trusts any incoming certificate. This is used for LDAPS connection.
